---

# 📋 **PLAN IMPLEMENTASI FITUR ABSENSI — AL-HASANAH ADMIN PANEL**

> **Versi:** 1.0 — *Disiapkan untuk review sebelum eksekusi*  
> **Tanggal:** 14 Juni 2026  
> **Status:** 🔍 **PLAN MODE** — Read-only, belum ada eksekusi

---

## 1. 🎯 **RINGKASAN KEBUTUHAN (Dari Diskusi)**

| Aspek | Keputusan |
|-------|-----------|
| **Tipe Absensi** | Hybrid: **Shalat Wajib (5x)** + **Sesi Akademik (Pagi/Siang/Sore)** |
| **Metode Input** | **QR Code Scan** (primary) + Manual by Ustadz (fallback) |
| **Status Kehadiran** | `HADIR`, `IZIN`, `SAKIT`, `ALPA`, `TERLAMBAT`, `CUTI`, `DISPENSASI`, `REPRESENTASI` |
| **Role Akses** | `kesantrian` (CRUD), `dewan` (Read-only rekap), `super_admin/rois` (Full) |
| **Export Rekap** | **Excel + PDF** (Batch/Kelas + Personal per santri) |
| **Format Tanggal** | **Indonesia Locale**: `"Senin, 14 Juni 2026"` |
| **Skalabilitas** | **Partitioning by month** + **Auto-archive via Edge Function** |

---

## 2. 🗄️ **ARsitektur DATABASE — PARTITIONING STRATEGY**

### 2.1 **Strategi: Native PostgreSQL Partitioning (Recommended)**

> **Mengapa bukan tabel terpisah manual (`absensi.01_06_2026`)?**
> - Native partitioning = **transparent ke aplikasi** (query tetap sama)
> - **Auto-maintenance** (no manual DDL per bulan)
> - **Partition pruning** otomatis oleh query planner
> - **Foreign key** ke tabel reference tetap bekerja
> - **Index** hanya perlu di parent, propagate ke partitions

```sql
-- ============================================================
-- 1. ENUM TYPES
-- ============================================================
CREATE TYPE attendance_status AS ENUM (
  'HADIR', 'IZIN', 'SAKIT', 'ALPA', 'TERLAMBAT', 
  'CUTI', 'DISPENSASI', 'REPRESENTASI'
);

CREATE TYPE session_type AS ENUM (
  -- Shalat Wajib
  'SHALAT_SUBUH', 'SHALAT_DHUHUR', 'SHALAT_ASHAR', 
  'SHALAT_MAGHRIB', 'SHALAT_ISYA',
  -- Akademik
  'AKADEMIK_PAGI', 'AKADEMIK_SIANG', 'AKADEMIK_SORE'
);

-- ============================================================
-- 2. PARENT TABLES (PARTITIONED)
-- ============================================================

-- Attendance Sessions (partitioned by RANGE on session_date)
CREATE TABLE attendance_sessions (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  session_date DATE NOT NULL,
  session_type session_type NOT NULL,
  kelas VARCHAR(10),              -- NULL = semua kelas
  jurusan VARCHAR(20),            -- NULL = semua jurusan
  starts_at TIME NOT NULL,
  ends_at TIME NOT NULL,
  qr_code_token VARCHAR(64) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
  qr_expires_at TIMESTAMPTZ,
  is_active BOOLEAN DEFAULT true,
  created_by UUID REFERENCES profiles(id),
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now(),
  updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
) PARTITION BY RANGE (session_date);

-- Student Attendance (partitioned by RANGE on session_date via FK)
CREATE TABLE santri_attendance (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  session_id UUID NOT NULL,       -- FK to attendance_sessions (per partition)
  santri_nis TEXT NOT NULL REFERENCES santri(nis) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  status attendance_status NOT NULL DEFAULT 'ALPA',
  check_in_at TIMESTAMPTZ,
  recorded_by UUID REFERENCES profiles(id),
  note TEXT,
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now(),
  updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now(),
  UNIQUE(session_id, santri_nis)
) PARTITION BY RANGE (session_date);  -- Virtual column via FK

-- ============================================================
-- 3. MONTHLY PARTITIONS (Auto-created by Edge Function)
-- ============================================================
-- Contoh: Partisi Juni 2026
CREATE TABLE attendance_sessions_2026_06 PARTITION OF attendance_sessions
  FOR VALUES FROM ('2026-06-01') TO ('2026-07-01');

CREATE TABLE santri_attendance_2026_06 PARTITION OF santri_attendance
  FOR VALUES FROM ('2026-06-01') TO ('2026-07-01');

-- ============================================================
-- 4. INDEXES (Di parent, auto-propagate ke partitions)
-- ============================================================
CREATE INDEX idx_attendance_sessions_date_type 
  ON attendance_sessions (session_date, session_type);

CREATE INDEX idx_attendance_sessions_qr_token 
  ON attendance_sessions (qr_code_token) 
  WHERE is_active = true;

CREATE INDEX idx_santri_attendance_session 
  ON santri_attendance (session_id);

CREATE INDEX idx_santri_attendance_santri_date 
  ON santri_attendance (santri_nis, session_date DESC);  -- session_date via join

CREATE INDEX idx_santri_attendance_status 
  ON santri_attendance (status);

-- ============================================================
-- 5. RLS POLICIES
-- ============================================================
ALTER TABLE attendance_sessions ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
ALTER TABLE santri_attendance ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;

-- Policy: Authenticated users can read
CREATE POLICY "auth_read_sessions" ON attendance_sessions
  FOR SELECT TO authenticated USING (true);

CREATE POLICY "auth_read_attendance" ON santri_attendance
  FOR SELECT TO authenticated USING (true);

-- Policy: kesantrian/rois/super_admin can manage
CREATE POLICY "kesantrian_manage_sessions" ON attendance_sessions
  FOR ALL TO authenticated 
  USING (auth.jwt() ->> 'role' IN ('kesantrian','rois','super_admin'))
  WITH CHECK (auth.jwt() ->> 'role' IN ('kesantrian','rois','super_admin'));

CREATE POLICY "kesantrian_manage_attendance" ON santri_attendance
  FOR ALL TO authenticated 
  USING (auth.jwt() ->> 'role' IN ('kesantrian','rois','super_admin'))
  WITH CHECK (auth.jwt() ->> 'role' IN ('kesantrian','rois','super_admin'));
```

### 2.2 **Edge Function: Auto-Partition Manager**

```typescript
// supabase/functions/attendance-partition-manager/index.ts
// Dijalankan via pg_cron setiap hari 1 bulan baru (00:05 WIB)

import { createClient } from 'npm:@supabase/supabase-js@2';

const supabase = createClient(
  Deno.env.get('SUPABASE_URL')!,
  Deno.env.get('SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY')!
);

async function ensureMonthlyPartitions() {
  const now = new Date();
  // Buat partisi untuk bulan ini + 2 bulan ke depan (buffer)
  for (let i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
    const target = new Date(now.getFullYear(), now.getMonth() + i, 1);
    const next = new Date(target.getFullYear(), target.getMonth() + 1, 1);

    const suffix = `${target.getFullYear()}_${String(target.getMonth() + 1).padStart(2, '0')}`;
    const from = target.toISOString().split('T')[0];
    const to = next.toISOString().split('T')[0];

    // Attendance Sessions Partition
    await supabase.rpc('exec_sql', {
      sql: `
        CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS attendance_sessions_${suffix} 
        PARTITION OF attendance_sessions 
        FOR VALUES FROM ('${from}') TO ('${to}');

        CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS santri_attendance_${suffix} 
        PARTITION OF santri_attendance 
        FOR VALUES FROM ('${from}') TO ('${to}');
      `
    });
  }
}

Deno.serve(async () => {
  try {
    await ensureMonthlyPartitions();
    return new Response(JSON.stringify({ ok: true, message: 'Partitions ensured' }), { status: 200 });
  } catch (e) {
    return new Response(JSON.stringify({ error: e.message }), { status: 500 });
  }
});
```

> **Catatan:** Fungsi `exec_sql` perlu dibuat terlebih dahulu (helper untuk DDL via RPC).

---

## 3. 📦 **TYPESCRIPT TYPES** (`src/types.tsx`)

```typescript
// ===== ABSENSI TYPES =====
export type AttendanceStatus = 
  | 'HADIR' | 'IZIN' | 'SAKIT' | 'ALPA' | 'TERLAMBAT' 
  | 'CUTI' | 'DISPENSASI' | 'REPRESENTASI';

export type SessionType = 
  | 'SHALAT_SUBUH' | 'SHALAT_DHUHUR' | 'SHALAT_ASHAR' 
  | 'SHALAT_MAGHRIB' | 'SHALAT_ISYA'
  | 'AKADEMIK_PAGI' | 'AKADEMIK_SIANG' | 'AKADEMIK_SORE';

export const SESSION_TYPE_LABELS: Record<SessionType, string> = {
  SHALAT_SUBUH: 'Shalat Subuh', SHALAT_DHUHUR: 'Shalat Dhuhur', 
